name: ThingSmartBLECoreKit
prefix_header_contents:
#ifdef __OBJC__

  #import <YYModel/YYModel.h>
  #import "ThingSmartBLECoreKit.h"
  #import "ThingBLECorePrivateConf.h"
  #import "ThingBLECoreNotificationKeys.h"
  #import "ThingSmartBLEActiveDelegate.h"
  #import <ThingBluetooth/ThingBluetooth.h>
  #import <ThingSmartUtil/ThingSmartUtil.h>
  
  #undef ThingLog
  #undef ThingSDKLogDebug
  #undef ThingSDKLogInfo
  #undef ThingSDKLogWarn
  #undef ThingSDKLogError
  #define ThingSDKLogDebug(...)         ThingSDKLog(0, @"ThingSmartBLECoreKit", @"", __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, __LINE__, ##__VA_ARGS__)
  #define ThingSDKLogInfo(...)         ThingSDKLog(1, @"ThingSmartBLECoreKit", @"", __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, __LINE__, ##__VA_ARGS__)
  #define ThingSDKLogWarn(...)         ThingSDKLog(2, @"ThingSmartBLECoreKit", @"", __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, __LINE__, ##__VA_ARGS__)
  #define ThingSDKLogError(...)         ThingSDKLog(3, @"ThingSmartBLECoreKit", @"", __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, __LINE__, ##__VA_ARGS__)
  #define ThingBLELogInfo(id, step, ...)       ThingSDKLogInfo(@"-> %@ -> %@ -> %@", id, step, __VA_ARGS__)

  #define TYBCoreLogDebug(...)         ThingSDKLog(0, @"ThingSmartBLECoreKit", @"", __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, __LINE__, ##__VA_ARGS__)
  #define ThingBCoreLogInfo(...)         ThingSDKLog(1, @"ThingSmartBLECoreKit", @"", __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, __LINE__, ##__VA_ARGS__)
  #define TYBCoreLogWarn(...)         ThingSDKLog(2, @"ThingSmartBLECoreKit", @"", __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, __LINE__, ##__VA_ARGS__)
  #define TYBCoreLogError(...)         ThingSDKLog(3, @"ThingSmartBLECoreKit", @"", __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, __LINE__, ##__VA_ARGS__)

#endif
